'''006  Ask how many slices of pizza the user started with and ask how many slices 
they have eaten. Work out how many slices they have left and display the answer in a user
friendly format. '''
pizza=int(input('How many slices of Pizza did you have?'))
pizza_2=int(input('How may slices have you eaten?'))
rem_pizza=pizza-pizza_2

if pizza_2>=pizza:
    print('Invalid answer')
else:
   print('You have',rem_pizza,'Pizza remaining')
   

